From 891118130143e9a78d7b87d932762753a149ba2c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Mon, 20 Jul 2026 08:29:29 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add design/price survey section after Partnership

Adds a survey section showing product design mockups and a suggested
price, collects purchase-intent and desired-price responses, and
gathers name/contact for a gifticon raffle with a PIPA-style privacy
consent block. Form submission is client-side (survey.js) and posts
to a configurable endpoint (e.g. Formspree) since the site is static.
---
 index.html | 102 ++++++++++++++++++++
 style.css  | 274 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 survey.js  |  75 +++++++++++++++
 3 files changed, 451 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 survey.js

